Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu: make sure that BOs have a backing store
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Patch-mainline: 6.4.4
References: bsc#1012628 bsc#1212848
